title: Colony NorthStar Credit: 1Q Earnings Snapshot
text:
LOS ANGELES (AP) _ Colony NorthStar Credit Real Estate Inc. (CLNC) on Tuesday reported a loss of $4.7 million in its first quarter.
The Los Angeles-based company said it had a loss of 5 cents per share. Earnings, adjusted for non-recurring costs, came to 44 cents per share.
The real estate investment trust posted revenue of $30.3 million in the period.
